Package clientGUI

Class CustomerServicesGUIController

  • java.lang.Object
    • clientGUI.CustomerServicesGUIController
  • public class CustomerServicesGUIController
extends java.lang.Object
    Customer Serves Controller - made for users from type "customer serves", the controller 2 buttons, user can "Insert complaint"/"Review Survey", if there is an error, a suitable message will be shown.

    Project Name: Zer-Li (Java Application Flower Store)

    Version:
    V1.00 2022
    Author:
    Habib Ibrahim, Vitaly Rofman, Ibrahim Daoud, Yosif Hosen
